{"tid":717670,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"信封上郵戳 已經由香港HONG KONG 變成中國香港  HONG KONG CHINA!","createTime":"2018-06-26T08:24:04.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-26T12:34:54.000Z","uid":33433,"like":1,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"014cfc64fb00426d9c88cdb90d2e9117f5393f79","tid":717670,"uid":33433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T08:24:04.000Z","msg":"政府公函 暫時都仲係 <br />\n<br />\n香港 郵資已付 HONG KONG postage paid<br />\n咁樣<br />\n<br />\n但某啲銀行寄黎嘅信已經變左 <br />\n<br />\n中國香港 HONG KONG CHINA<br />\n<br />\n轉左嘅銀行有 大新銀行，中銀保誠 <br />\n共通點都係紅底機構？<br />\n<br />\n匯豐銀行前日寄黎嘅信係只有英文postage paid字樣<br />\n<br />\n補圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/26/162312_cdb9323fb67a6c3f1ae7d7c7fd756e2e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F26%2F162312_cdb9323fb67a6c3f1ae7d7c7fd756e2e.png&h=f0a5d87b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n支那又從日常生活洗香港人腦了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76b60eb061c33ddc2d9fb827a15e989dc01ffc00","tid":717670,"uid":36441,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T08:29:53.000Z","msg":"如果海外寄黎就慘 比大陸拖返幾個禮拜先掉返落黎"},{"pid":"9ec0b72d1cd6bfac704245cc13ade69fffad3854","tid":717670,"uid":20227,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T08:31:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0628a7d53425b02fe317c6459f4247862297e81e","tid":717670,"uid":3241,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T08:50:18.000Z","msg":"正常人都知寄香港一定唔可以愛支那<br />\n除非你封信想輪迴幾次先到手"},{"pid":"87801bad6a708fe94c4f1583780d630aaffbcfcc","tid":717670,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0628a7d53425b02fe317c6459f4247862297e81e","tid":717670,"uid":3241,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T08:50:18.000Z","msg":"正常人都知寄香港一定唔可以愛支那<br />\n除非你封信想輪迴幾次先到手"},"citedBy":0,"rep